Message:
The prince punished the horrible
man and his accomplices.
And with that, I was finally
released from the estate.

All the poor, imprisoned women
were also able to return
to their homes.

I’m a witch, so I have no home
to go back to...but that’s fine.

Because I get to stay
with my prince—

The love of my life that
even appeared to me
in my dreams.

Hehehe... Ahh...
this warm and fuzzy feeling...
So this is true love.

I will always
love you, my prince.
